description: The Fund seeks daily investment results, before fees and expenses, of 2 times (200%) the daily percentage change of the common stock of Apple, (NASDAQ: AAPL) There is no guarantee that the Fund will meet its stated objective. The fund should not be expected to provide 2 times the cumulative return of AAPL for periods greater than a day.
name: GraniteShares 2x Long AAPL Daily ETF
